These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, amaryllis, rose
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red, azure
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, techno
3 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, mah-jongg
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, havana, aristoff
 1. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 2. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking water is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the havana-smoker is the person who growsrose##1
 6. the aristoff-smoker is the person drinking water##1
 7. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |       3       |
| Flower          | rose       | orchid   | amaryllis      |
| Color           | azure | yellow      | blood-red      |
| Beverage   | lemonade        | water        | juice  |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | classical     | funk          |
| Game   | billiard      | scrabble        | mah-jongg       |
| Cigar         | havana       | aristoff | chaman |

