.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-2::.
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, wooden
There 3 different types of food: apple, cherry, papaya
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, airplane, snowmobile
City: san-francisco, london, hamburg
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, cain, chaman
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, badminton, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 3. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 5. the wooden house is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
 6. the person traveling to london is between the chaman-smoker and the person eating papaya##2
 7. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the art-deco house is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |      3      |
| House      | art-deco        | wooden        | gothic-revival |
| Food          | papaya       | cherry       | apple       |
| Transport         | airplane   | snowmobile      | boat      |
| City           | hamburg | london | san-francisco     |
| Cigar   | bolivar    | cain        | chaman        |
| Sport           | snowboarding        | biathlon         | badminton        |

