.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, engineer, nurse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, orchid, poppy
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, polish, american
3 different games are played: chess, billiard, mah-jongg
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hamster
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, dannemann, oliveros
1. the person who growsorchid is the russian##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
3. the oliveros-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the manager##2
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the american##1
5. the owner of the hamster is the russian##1
6. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
7. the nurse is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
8. the engineer is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3       |
| Job          | manager   | nurse   | engineer        |
| Flower         | aconite | poppy  | orchid      |
| Nationality   | polish     | american | russian       |
| Game   | chess        | mah-jongg   | billiard       |
| Pet           | guinea-pig  | bird     | hamster      |
| Cigar         | baccarat      | oliveros   | dannemann |

