.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, september, october
City: nizza, miami, new-york
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite, sunflower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, metal
House: ranch-style, townhouse, art-deco
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, grapefruit, cucumber
 1. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
 2. the person eating grapefruit is the ranch-style house##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the person traveling to nizza##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
 7. the fan of metal is the person eating nectarine##1
 8. the fan of classical is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to miami##2
 9. the art-deco house is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growssunflower##2
10. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
11. the ranch-style house is the person eating grapefruit##1
12. the person who growssunflower is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Birthday      | september     | march | october              |
| City         | nizza   | new-york | miami          |
| Flower           | sunflower   | marigold       | aconite |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | classical   | metal              |
| House   | ranch-style | art-deco     | townhouse           |
| Food     | grapefruit    | cucumber       | nectarine               |

