The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, ice-hockey
 1. the accountant is the old-henry-smoker##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes ebony##1
 6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 9. the person playing bridge is the police-officer##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |      3      |
| Color      | ebony       | purple          | green       |
