The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, d&b, jazz
3 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, pony
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, march, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 4. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
 5. the musician is the person playing snooker##1
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is the fan of jazz##1
 7. the scientist is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is the fan of jazz##1
11. the entrepreneur is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
12. the person playing scrabble is the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |
