 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person eating grapefruit##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is the chaman-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
 6. the dannemann-smoker is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 9. the person eating grapefruit is the owner of the cat##1
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the owner of the cat is the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |       2       |     3     |
| Transport      | van     | scooter | snowmobile       |
