.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-18::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, trike
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, scientific, western
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, light-blue, mauve
City: london, miami, paris
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, lily, begonia
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, hot-chocolate
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is the person traveling to paris##1
 3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who growsbegonia##1
 6. the person who likes black is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
 8. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the person driving the airplane is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Transport         | airplane      | snowmobile    | trike     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | western    | scientific |
| Color   | light-blue        | black | mauve     |
| City   | london       | paris       | miami   |
| Flower           | balloon-flower   | begonia     | lily       |
| Beverage         | iced-tea     | hot-chocolate | cola    |

