.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-19::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, poppy, rose
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, december, september
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, r&b
City: colone, venice, new-york
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, amber, lilac
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, manager, bartender
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the bartender is the fan of funk##1
5. the pilot is between the person traveling to new-york and the person who growspoppy##2
6. the bartender is on the far right##1
7. the pilot is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
8. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
9. the person who likes amber is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who growsballoon-flower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |
| Flower      | poppy   | rose    | balloon-flower |
| Birthday   | december     | march | september     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | r&b         | funk        |
| City   | venice    | colone     | new-york    |
| Color           | blood-red | amber    | lilac      |
| Job         | manager   | pilot    | bartender      |

