.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, aquamarine, brown
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, october, april
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, french, polish
3 different games are played: bridge, go, scrabble
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, parkour
City: paris, boston, colone
1. the person who likes brown is the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the polish is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
4. the person who likes orange is the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person who likes brown is the person playing go##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
7. the french is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person playing scrabble is between the polish and the person traveling to boston##2
9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |         2          |       3       |
| Color          | orange     | aquamarine              | brown        |
| Birthday           | september | april | october |
| Nationality   | french      | italian             | polish    |
| Game   | bridge         | scrabble               | go          |
| Sport         | badminton   | parkour            | ice-hockey    |
| City     | boston   | colone               | paris           |

 